---
title: Honey Lime Spiced Chicken with Bulgur Kidney Bean Pilaf
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Honey Lime Spiced Chicken in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-lime-spiced-chicken-0a6279e6-661be69b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/honey-lime-spiced-chicken-5ee210d2e6057361e20ca125-91bf1179.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 589 kcal
  fat: 16 g
  saturated fat: 5 g
  carbohydrates: 68 g
